+## v4.1 governance and telemetry layer
+
+This package keeps the hot wire invariant and extends TriTRPC v4 with:
+
+- route-level governance and observability defaults;
+- telemetry profiles, redaction profiles, and retention profiles;
+- widened chained event records for control-plane observability;
+- typed beacon semantic deltas for CAP / INTENT / COMMIT lanes;
+- derived operational views such as run cards and policy posture reports.
